#: includes/admin-actions-page.php:140
msgid "Give your chatbot the ability to do things — generate images, search the web, hand off to a human, capture an email, and more. There are two ways to set this up. The cards below explain when to use each."
msgstr ""

#: includes/admin-actions-page.php:149
msgid "Two ways to set up actions"
msgstr ""

#: includes/admin-actions-page.php:152
msgid "Both let your chatbot take action during a conversation. Pick whichever fits how you want it to behave — or use both together."
